ss=\"flex flex-col gap-0.5\"><div class=\"flex items-baseline gap-1\"><span class=\"text-xl font-bold\" style=\"color:#22c55e\">3 000 XAF</span><span class=\"text-zinc-500 text-xs\">/mois</span></div></div><p class=\"mt-3 text-zinc-400 text-xs leading-relaxed\">Plan de démarrage pour les petites entreprises. Essai gratuit inclus !</p></div><ul class=\"space-y-3 mb-8 flex-1\"><li class=\"flex items-start gap-2.5 text-zinc-300 text-xs\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check h-4 w-4 text-green-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg><span>1 instance WhatsApp</span></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-2.5 text-zinc-300 text-xs\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check h-4 w-4 text-green-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg><span>Envois illimités</span></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-2.5 text-zinc-300 text-xs\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check h-4 w-4 text-green-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg><span>Accès API REST</span></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-2.5 text-zinc-300 text-xs\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-